<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.98552.figure33>
    dc:description "Figure 33. The ecological habitat photographs of Cavariella in field A the apterae and nymphs of Cavariella japonica (Essig & Kuwana) feeding on tender stem of Salix B, C the apterae and nymphs of Cavariella japonica feeding on tender stem of Apiaceae D the apterae and nymphs of Cavariella konoi Takahashi feeding on the leaves of Salix." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/880480" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

